{"id":866,"date":"2017-12-22T02:36:51","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T02:36:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=866"},"modified":"2021-02-27T09:47:49","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T09:47:49","slug":"phong-cach-hien-dai-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-hien-dai-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that\/","title":{"rendered":"Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean xa x\u1ec9 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng gi\u1eefa trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp. V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi m\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n ngay t\u1eeb khi b\u1ea1n mua ch\u00fang?<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">Phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u k\u00ec di\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong> B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i? <\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 th\u1ee9 19. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh Cung th\u1ee7y tinh (Crystal Palace) \u1edf Hyde Park (Lu\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4n \u2013 Anh) n\u0103m 1851, do ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Joseph Paxton thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i t\u01b0 duy m\u1edbi trong x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00fac b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec7t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n. Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ra \u0111\u1eddi t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-868 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"934\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai.jpg 934w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-300x247.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-768x632.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 934px) 100vw, 934px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(<em>Cung th\u1ee7y tinh (Crystal Palace) &#8211; ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Joseph Paxton<\/em>)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u00fac ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 20 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 XX v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cho nhi\u1ec1u l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u0103m 1919, m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng Bauhaus (\u0110\u1ee9c) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u2013 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-870\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1.png 1080w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-768x576.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-1-1024x768.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(Ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 mang phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; a. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0u s\u1eafc:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><em>Gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh (m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, be, n\u00e2u, \u0111en) \u2013 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u theo t\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o mang l\u1ea1i rung c\u1ea3m m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-871\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2.png 1500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2-768x576.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-2-1024x768.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0: chrome, k\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-872\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-3.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-3-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, k\u00ednh d\u1ec5 t\u00ecm trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian: <\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p <strong><em>s\u1ef1 k\u00eat h\u1ee3p 2 trong 1<\/em><\/strong> (ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp) th\u00ec phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft \u0103n nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi nhau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch logic t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn th\u00f4ng su\u1ed1t, h\u1ee3p l\u00ed cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf li\u00ean th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nhau c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-873\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4.jpg 5472w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 5472px) 100vw, 5472px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(Kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch li\u00ean th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n (c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng v\u00e0 r\u00e8m) \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfu qua t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;d. \u0110\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0 mang phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t gi\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3c thanh tho\u00e1t v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt khi \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch m\u00e0u ghi xanh, h\u00e3y s\u01a1n n\u00f3 l\u00ean b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh hay ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc b\u00e0n m\u00e0u ghi xanh. M\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea3ng l\u1edbn, h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-874\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-5.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-5-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-5-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-5-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">(Nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u m\u1ea1nh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n, l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng , t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n v\u1edbi gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ea7n v\u00e0 s\u00e0n)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh theo phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u01b0u ti\u00ean gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh : x\u00e1m, tr\u1eafng, \u0111en l\u00e0 gam m\u00e0u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng cho kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf: <\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0: k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi 1 gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm, \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i x\u01b0ng. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n ngh\u1ecb, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian, thanh l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u k\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi ti\u1ebft hay thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh tr\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn \u201ct\u00e1n d\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d c\u00f9ng th\u00edch th\u00fa c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean xa x\u1ec9 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng gi\u1eefa trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp. V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"a